  {
    "speaker": "interviewee",
    "tag": "HK",
    "text": "Yes, those are my parents, my sisters-- my oldest sister, Elsa, my father, Joseph, my mother, Martha, my little sister, Ruth. Was taken in 1941 in Mirabeau, France, during the war. That was the last picture I ever had from them.",
